wikipedia_page.main: Jocelyn Ulyett (born 17 September 1995) is a British professional swimmer. She is also British record holder in the short-course 200m breaststroke. Having accomplished this at the Swim England Winter Championships 2019 with a time of 2.17.10, she then went on to set the 100m short-course English record.
